* Self-made PBO sample for this repository.
* This file is intentionally tiny and may be redistributed with this project.
* #variable= 3 #constraint= 2
*
* Choose at least one item while respecting a small capacity.
* Minimize the negated profit, so the optimum is the highest profit feasible set.
min: -3 x1 -2 x2 -4 x3 ;
+1 x1 +1 x2 +1 x3 >= 1 ;
+2 x1 +1 x2 +3 x3 <= 3 ;
